   scanKeyDetails: key 1: [(isInequality: false, estimatedEntryCount: 100), (isInequality: false, estimatedEntryCount: 100)]
   ->  Index Scan using a_1 on documents_1701 collection (actual rows=1 loops=1)
         Index Cond: (document @= '{ "a" : "" }'::bson)
         Rows Removed by Index Recheck: 99
(13 rows)

